## Verify Ollama

### Start Ollama:
ollama serve

### Check version:
curl.exe http://localhost:11434/api/version

### Check installed models:
ollama list

### Test model:
python test.py


## Run Backend
cd ai-backend
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
uvicorn main:app

## Voice Commands

### Start microphone listener:
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:8000/voice/start

### Check status:
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:8000/voice/status

### Stop listener:
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:8000/voice/stop


## Othere commands

Test Chat
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:8000/chat `
  -Body (@{message='Hello Jarvis'} | ConvertTo-Json) `
  -ContentType 'application/json'
Test Intent Detection
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:8000/intent `
  -Body (@{message='Add a task to learn Docker tomorrow'} | ConvertTo-Json) `
  -ContentType 'application/json'
Test Task Creation
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:8000/voice/command `
  -Body (@{message='Add a task to learn Docker tomorrow'} | ConvertTo-Json) `
  -ContentType 'application/json'
View Tasks
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get `
